item.name: RabbitMQ Message Deliver Get Rates
item.description: Sum of: - deliver: Count of messages delivered in acknowledgement mode to consumers. - deliver_noack: Count of messages delivered in no-acknowledgement mode to consumers. - get: Count of messages delivered in acknowledgement mode in response to basic.get. - get_noack: Count of messages delivered in no-acknowledgement mode in response to basic.get.

item.name: RabbitMQ Message Deliver No Ack Rates
item.description: Count of messages delivered in no-acknowledgement mode to consumers.

item.name: RabbitMQ Message Get Rates
item.description: Count of messages delivered in acknowledgement mode in response to basic.get.

item.name: RabbitMQ Message Publish In Rates
item.description: Count of messages published "in" to an exchange, i.e. not taking account of routing.

item.name: RabbitMQ Message Publish Out Rates
item.description: Count of messages published "out" of an exchange, i.e. taking account of routing.

item.name: RabbitMQ Message Publish Rates
item.description: This is the number of messages published _to_ the rabbitmq server

item.name: RabbitMQ Message Redeliver Rates
item.description: Count of subset of messages in deliver_get which had the redelivered flag set.

item.name: RabbitMQ Message Return Rates
item.description: Count of messages returned to publisher as unroutable.
